"...for by thy sorceries were all nations deceived." Revelation 18:23

"Wherein in time past ye walked according to the course of this world, according to the prince of the power of the air, the spirit that now worketh in the children of disobedience:" 
Ephesians 2:2
From as far back as mankind can remember, there has always been an evil which pervaded our world. A darkness so malevolent, that God Himself had to speak words of light in order to push it back. But when sin entered the world through Adam, the forces of witchcraft were allowed to have legal access to humanity. This video is an exploration and an expose' of the satanic operations which control the systems of this world. The good news is that Jesus has made a way for God's children to overcome the powers of darkness. We have three powerful weapons: 
1)The name of Jesus
2)The blood of Jesus
3)The word of God (The sword of the Spirit)


Please check out the Worldshare Foundation website: 

www.worldshare.com

Worldshare Foundation is a charity committed to easing the suffering of God's children in Kenya and Uganda. We at Life Is Spiritual Ministries want to thank everyone who has so generously donated to this worthy cause. Your gift has gone a long way to help feed many families, and this is just the beginning! With your help, we can eliminate hunger, starvation and untimely death from the entire village. 

Proverbs 19:17 "He that is gracious to the poor lends unto Jehovah; and what he has bestowed will he repay unto him."

          This is how we lay up for ourselves treasures in Heaven. When Erica died and went to Heaven, she saw many people who were pleading with the Father to allow them to go back to the earth and do what they were supposed to do. 

Matthew 6:19-21 "Lay not up for yourselves treasures upon earth, where moth and rust does corrupt, and where thieves break through and steal: 20 But lay up for yourselves treasures in Heaven, where neither moth nor rust does corrupt, and where thieves do not break through nor steal; 21 For where your treasure is, there will your heart be also."

snippet.title: SPIDER-MAN against TUNG TUNG TUNG SAHUR on Motorcycle in RAINBOW SPIDERS BRIDGE | GTA MULTIVERSE
snippet.description:
SPIDER-MAN against TUNG TUNG TUNG SAHUR on Motorcycle in RAINBOW SPIDERS BRIDGE | GTA MULTIVERSE

Hi, it’s KeFresh here!
Get ready for one of the craziest GTA 5 stunt challenges ever — packed with danger, chaos, and insane moments! 💥🔥

The race begins on the wild Curved Spider McQueen Bridge, twisting high above the water, where one wrong move can send you flying straight into the waves.
But that’s just the start…
The unstoppable TUNG TUNG TUNG SAHUR is back, the terrifying Scary Head Train is rushing through the track, and chaos is taking over! 🚂💣

Our heroes jump into the action on motorcycles, cars, boats, quad bikes, and helicopters, racing across one of the most intense maps ever made! 🚗🏍️🚁🛥️
And don’t forget — under the bridge, the SPIDER SHARK is waiting for anyone who falls! 🦈😱

This is a true epic stunt race challenge — full of traps, explosions, and pure adrenaline.
Let’s go — KeFresh style! 🕷️🚀🔥

snippet.title: Diamond Platnumz - Nani (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Get The Song👇👇👇
https://dplatnumz.lnk.to/nani

In “Nani,” Diamond Platnumz flips the script with a playful love story set in a school — where he stars as a charming teacher who can’t help but fall for the newly appointed teacher. The chemistry is instant, the tension is real, and the visuals bring his flirtatious lyrics to life. In the song, Diamond pours his heart out, saying he has no reason to look elsewhere because she’s his everything. With witty, seductive lines and his signature humor — even admitting how she drives him wild whenever she dresses sexy — Diamond delivers a smooth Bongo Flava anthem about love, temptation, and loyalty. “Nani” is more than a song; it’s a flirt-filled classroom romance told the Diamond Platnumz way — confident, funny, and irresistibly charming.
